{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I won a stipulated judgment for $150,000, not $50,000.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I decided to reduce it to $90,000, providing, providing they pay a certain way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, I don't want to get paid in 20 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I want to get paid a $50,000 check in a lump sum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You offered me a $50,000 reward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I want that $50,000 check.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And by the way, it's to be made out to Mel Mermelstein, personally, cashier's check.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, they first didn't agree.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Finally, they did agree.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then I said there's one more thing I want.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I want a letter of apology from you, not only to Mel Mermelstein, the Auschwitz survivor, but all other Auschwitz survivors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we got that, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That rang a bell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I got paid for the first $50,000. 30 days later, I got another $20,000. 30 days after that, another $20,000 cashier's check, which came seven days late.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I wasn't so very happy about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then there was a, well, a complaint filed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally my lawyers came out with an additional $38.36 in late charges.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they paid that, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what else?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What else do you want from them?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are you finished with that lawsuit then?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank God it finally-- we finally finished, because there's a lot more to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally finished in 1991-- 1992.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We won, because they sued me for another $3 and 1/2-- they sued me for $3 and 1/2 million, and then I answered the complaint, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they dismissed the complaint.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some, you know, back-and-forth disputes going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the law firm that filed that lawsuit against me for $3 and 1/2 million on their behalf settled.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
